Check quotes style:
	grep -Rn "[A-Za-z]'[A-Za-z]" src include
	grep -Rn ' "[A-Za-z]' src include
	grep -Rn '[A-Za-z]" ' src include

Check that initializations are done using constructor syntax instead of assignment:
	grep -Rn ' [_A-Za-z0-9]\+ = ' src include

Check that integer conversions donâ€™t use static_cast:
	grep -Rn 'static_cast<[_ 0-9A-Za-z]\+>' src include

